{"tid":1685690,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政務司辦公室男助理文書主任 涉旺角參與非法集會被捕","createTime":"2019-10-31T16:31:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T16:44:15.000Z","uid":222970,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"28e1c9112ada162c5bf71d22807d27fd864480f6","tid":1685690,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T16:31:21.000Z","msg":"今晚是蒙面惡法實施以來首個萬聖節，亦為8.31港鐵太子站恐襲事件兩個月，多名市民聚集在旺角警署外，未幾再一次爆發嚴重警民衝突，防暴警狂射催淚彈，並拘捕多名男女。據知，其中一名被捕男子為政務司司長辦公室的助理文書主任，他涉嫌今晚在旺角區參與非法集會而被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【抗暴之戰】政務司辦公室男助理文書主任 涉旺角參與非法集會被捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191101&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60217936\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191101%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60217936&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eCLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=8b45552f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191101%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60217936&h=dc301eb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191101&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60217936</a>"},{"pid":"41f11226fcb3b9af2b6ad9ce70980dc9c8669458","tid":1685690,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T16:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6fe1bb950477fbb0c72a95d331751c9ff0986a8","tid":1685690,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T16:32:19.000Z","msg":"留名等睇低調放人 大陸官媒一定唔敢報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ee8e91b410c067caba2ecabfbb1466b8b25e60","tid":1685690,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35aca44b48214e173f89a7b38c9609bfeda41fd8","tid":1685690,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T16:44:15.000Z","msg":"雖然希望佢係